Package: voice-training-data-creator
Version: 1.0.13
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-venv, python3-pyqt6, python3-numpy, libportaudio2
Maintainer: Daniel Rosehill <public@danielrosehill.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/danielrosehill/Voice-Training-Data-Creator
Description: Voice training data creation tool
 A GUI application for creating voice training datasets with synthetic
 text generation. Features include high-quality audio recording,
 AI-powered text generation, multiple style options, and custom
 vocabulary support.
 .
 This tool helps create consistent, high-quality voice datasets for
 training TTS (Text-to-Speech) and STT (Speech-to-Text) models.
